name: Eloquent Software
body:
Eloquent provides free, high quality, open-source software components and applications for public use. These projects are the result of many crazy ideas, sleepless nights, intense discussions, and hard working people. We hope you find them useful!

> The finest eloquence is that which gets things done.
>
> *- David Lloyd George*
